For each of the {= country =} in-scope countries ({= country_scope =}), name {= country_provider =}+ last-mile postal or parcel delivery providers per country. For each provider, supply all {= evidence_type =} evidence types listed below — with a source ({= url =}+ URL per (country, provider, evidence-type)).

